 5px; transition: 0.2s; }

.share-button:hover { transform: scale(1.1); filter: brightness(1.2); }

.share-button.linkedin { background-color: rgb(0, 119, 181); }

.share-button i { margin-right: 5px; font-size: 1.1em; }

